item.title: PI - cache doesnt unzip
item.dc:creator: @RegalX RegalX
item.description:
@RegalX wrote:

Did you package the cache alright yes? You need to highlight all the files in the cache folder and add them to archive, don’t make the FOLDER the archive, but the files inside. And make sure your archive file is a .zip and not .rar . Also, did you upload your cache into your public dropbox, and did you let it fully upload. I know these are incredibly easy and seem obvious but usually it’s the small things that get you
